{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. FITTS HOUSE - RICKY'S BEDROOM - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: On VIDEO: JANE BURNHAM lays in bed, wearing a tank top.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She's sixteen, with dark, intense eyes.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JANE
{DIALOGUE}: I need a father who's a role model, not some horny geek-boy who's gonna spray his shorts whenever I bring a girlfriend home from school.
{META_DATA}: (snorts)
{DIALOGUE}: What a lame-o.
{DIALOGUE}: Somebody really should put him out of his misery.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Her mind wanders for a beat.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RICKY (O.C.)
{DIALOGUE}: Want me to kill him for you?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jane looks at us and sits up.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JANE
{META_DATA}: (deadpan)
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, would you?
{META_DATA}: FADE TO BLACK.
{META_DATA}: FADE IN:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. ROBIN HOOD TRAIL - EARLY MORNING
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We're FLYING above suburban America, DESCENDING SLOWLY toward a tree-lined street.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LESTER (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: My name is Lester Burnham.
{DIALOGUE}: This is my neighborhood.
{DIALOGUE}: This is my street.
{DIALOGUE}: This... is my life.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm forty-two years old.
{DIALOGUE}: In less than a year, I'll be dead.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. BURNHAM HOUSE - MASTER BEDROOM - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We're looking down at a king-sized BED from OVERHEAD:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LESTER BURNHAM lies sleeping amidst expensive bed linens, face down, wearing PAJAMAS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An irritating ALARM CLOCK RINGS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lester gropes blindly to shut it off.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LESTER (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: Of course, I don't know that yet.
{DIALOGUE}: He rolls over, looks up at us and sighs.
{DIALOGUE}: He doesn't seem too thrilled at the prospect of a new day.
{META_DATA}: (CONTINUED)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 2.
{META_DATA}: CONTINUED:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LESTER (V.O.) (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: And in a way, I'm dead already.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He sits up and puts on his slippers.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. BURNHAM HOUSE - MASTER BATH - MOMENTS LATER
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lester thrusts his face directly into a steaming hot shower.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE from outside the shower: Lester's naked body is silhouetted through the fogged-up glass door.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It becomes apparent he is masturbating.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LESTER (V.O.)
{META_DATA}: (amused)
{DIALOGUE}: Look at me, jerking off in the shower.
{META_DATA}: (then)
{DIALOGUE}: This will be the high point of my day.
{DIALOGUE}: It's all downhill from here.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. BURNHAM HOUSE - MOMENTS LATER
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE on a single, dewy AMERICAN BEAUTY ROSE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A gloved hand with CLIPPERS appears and SNIPS the flower off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CAROLYN BURNHAM tends her rose bushes in front of the Burnham house.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A very well-put together woman of forty, she wears color-coordinated gardening togs and has lots of useful and expensive tools.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lester watches her through a WINDOW on the first floor, peeping out through the drapes.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LESTER (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: That's my wife Carolyn.
{DIALOGUE}: See the way the handle on those pruning shears matches her gardening clogs?
{DIALOGUE}: That's not an accident.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. JIMS' HOUSE - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In the fenced front yard of the house next door, a dog BARKS repeatedly.
