{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We HEAR the CAR HORN again from outside.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jane studies herself in a mirror, then shifts to get a good profile of her breasts.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. BURNHAM HOUSE - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Carolyn stands next to a platinum-colored MERCEDES-BENZ ML320, reaching in through the drivers' window to blow the HORN again.
