{DIALOGUE}: Yes.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CAROLYN
{DIALOGUE}: Well, congratulations.
{DIALOGUE}: You've succeeded admirably.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jane gets in the car.
