{CHARACTER_NAME}: RICKY (O.C.)
{DIALOGUE}: Because it's beautiful.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: On VIDEO: Angela looks at Jane, trying not to laugh.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANGELA
