{DIALOGUE}: It's okay.
{DIALOGUE}: I'll walk.
{DIALOGUE}: But thanks.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANGELA
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, see?
{DIALOGUE}: He doesn't want to go anyway.
{DIALOGUE}: C'mon, let's go.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Angela starts off, but Jane doesn't follow.
