{DIALOGUE}: No, I'm glad because you're old enough now to learn the most important lesson in life: you cannot count on anyone except yourself.
{META_DATA}: (sighs)
{DIALOGUE}: You cannot count on anyone except yourself.
{DIALOGUE}: It's sad, but true, and the sooner you learn it, the better.
{META_DATA}: (CONTINUED)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 64.
{META_DATA}: CONTINUED:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JANE
