{DIALOGUE}: When I was your age, I lived in a duplex.
{DIALOGUE}: We didn't even have our own house.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Embarrassed, she quickly leaves.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jane looks in a mirror and rubs her cheek, then crosses to the window and looks out.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. FITTS HOUSE - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jane's POV: We're across from Ricky's room, looking in.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He stands at the window with his DIGICAM, videotaping us.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: On the WIDE-SCREEN TV behind him, we see Jane standing in her window as she looks across at him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She waves.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Ricky just keeps videotaping.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A beat, then she starts to take off her shirt.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. FITTS HOUSE - RICKY'S BEDROOM - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We're behind Ricky as he videotapes Jane in her window.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She has now removed her shirt.
